WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.302
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.302 --> 00:00:04.851
I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:04.851 --> 00:00:05.996
Look at this.

00:00:05.996 --> 00:00:07.418
This is our prayer.

00:00:07.418 --> 00:00:11.160
This is what we were interceding for last night.

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:39.296
Whenever we were praying, there wasn't even rain in the forecast, and all of a sudden, it just started raining.

00:00:40.316 --> 00:00:51.390
I could hear the thunder, and we got almost an inch of rain.

00:00:51.390 --> 00:01:00.134
This is supernatural rain, ladies and gentlemen.

00:01:00.134 --> 00:01:18.039
When you pray and you believe, all things are possible to him that believes—even the weather.

00:01:18.039 --> 00:01:31.184
I just wanted to come on here; I'm excited about it.

00:01:31.184 --> 00:01:50.200
I wanted to show you what happens when you believe God for something.

00:01:50.200 --> 00:02:04.550
Rain is a big deal for us because it's been really dry.

00:02:04.980 --> 00:02:22.352
I just thought, 'I wanted to come on and show you our prayers are working.

00:02:22.352 --> 00:02:35.966
' It's amazing for the farmers, for the drought, for all of it.

00:02:35.966 --> 00:02:48.980
We're going to believe some more tonight.

00:02:54.360 --> 00:03:01.783
I asked the Lord for three inches, but we almost got an inch.

00:03:01.783 --> 00:03:08.119
It's a work in progress.

00:03:08.119 --> 00:03:27.458
Sometimes you see the olive branch and the dove's beak before you get the full manifestation.

00:03:27.458 --> 00:03:57.795
Like Noah, he sent the dove out and it brought back an olive branch, showing him the flood was over, the storm was over.

00:03:57.795 --> 00:04:13.116
I'm telling you, that's the way it will be in your life.

00:04:13.116 --> 00:04:14.856
Believe God.

00:04:14.856 --> 00:04:34.086
Even if you see first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation, never give up on what you're believing for.

00:04:44.564 --> 00:04:59.960
You may see just a little bit of something, just like I saw almost an inch, but I'm believing God for over three inches.

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:19.293
I want to go four or five inches to break the drought so that we're not in one anymore.

00:05:19.293 --> 00:05:25.928
These are exciting times.

00:05:30.497 --> 00:05:37.569
I have such an expectation in my spirit today.

00:05:37.569 --> 00:06:02.969
There's a stirring inside of me; something is happening in the realm of the spirit as we're praying together.

00:06:14.923 --> 00:06:18.289
I can feel it.

00:06:18.289 --> 00:06:39.462
Tonight, when I was sitting there talking to the Lord, I felt a fire, like when you're stoking a fireplace.

00:06:40.609 --> 00:06:45.617
I can feel it turning.

00:06:46.106 --> 00:06:57.181
I said, 'Holy Spirit, there's something going on.

00:06:57.181 --> 00:07:08.173
' We're moving the mountain, y'all.

00:07:08.173 --> 00:07:16.319
Faith will move a mountain.

00:07:16.319 --> 00:07:45.595
The Bible says it in Mark 11:23 and 24: 'Whatsoever things you desire, when you pray, believe that you receive them, and you shall have them.

00:07:45.595 --> 00:08:13.079
If you say to the mountain, "Be thou removed and be thou cast into the sea," and shall not doubt in your heart, you shall have whatsoever things you say.

00:08:13.079 --> 00:08:17.578
' I want to encourage you all: don't give up on what you're believing for.

00:08:28.840 --> 00:08:39.159
When I was praying this evening, the Lord said, 'Brandon, I want you to tell those old testimonies you've told before.

00:08:39.159 --> 00:09:19.800
' I told you all a couple of videos ago about the dog being raised from the dead and my little girl praying for that dog in the hall.

00:09:19.800 --> 00:09:28.620
All things are possible to him who believes.

00:09:28.620 --> 00:09:33.035
I'm going to tell you another testimony of what happened to me.

00:09:39.226 --> 00:09:54.600
I was mowing my grandmother's yard—I mowed her grass all the time—and there was this African-American man walking down the road.

00:09:54.600 --> 00:10:14.396
He would walk a couple of feet and stop, breathing really hard.

00:10:14.396 --> 00:10:31.665
I thought, 'Wow, that's sad,' but I just kept mowing.

00:10:31.665 --> 00:10:51.320
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I want you to go pray for that man.

00:10:51.320 --> 00:11:06.359
' I said, 'You want me to go pray for that man?

00:11:06.359 --> 00:11:15.800
' I ignored it, to be real with y'all.

00:11:18.535 --> 00:11:36.480
I thought, 'I don't know that man; I'm not going to go pray for him.

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:47.535
' I just started mowing some more.

00:11:47.535 --> 00:12:10.943
He got closer, and the Lord said, 'Are you going to obey me and go pray for that man?

00:12:10.943 --> 00:12:28.990
' I reasoned it out in my mind, thinking that man probably wouldn't want me praying for him.

00:12:28.990 --> 00:12:55.286
That's your flesh trying to talk you out of it through fear or intimidation.

00:13:00.187 --> 00:13:15.468
The devil tries to whisper in your ear to discourage you.

00:13:23.639 --> 00:13:50.730
The man got right up to me, and the Lord said sternly, 'Are you going to obey me and go pray for that man?

00:13:50.730 --> 00:14:00.815
' I said, 'Father, I'm sorry.

00:14:00.815 --> 00:14:07.910
I'll go pray for him.

00:14:07.910 --> 00:14:30.669
' I turned the mower off and said, 'Sir, can I talk to you for a second?

00:14:30.669 --> 00:14:42.024
' He stopped and looked at me.

00:14:42.024 --> 00:14:49.000
I noticed his skin was ashy.

00:14:49.000 --> 00:14:59.769
He looked very pale and gray, not healthy.

00:15:16.959 --> 00:15:20.888
He had tubes in his nose and an oxygen tank he was dragging behind him.

00:15:29.479 --> 00:15:31.160
I asked, 'How are you doing today?

00:15:31.160 --> 00:15:44.519
' He said, 'I'm not doing good.

00:15:44.519 --> 00:15:47.120
I'm dying.

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:57.090
' I asked what the problem was.

00:15:57.090 --> 00:16:07.600
He said, 'I need a lung transplant.

00:16:07.600 --> 00:16:28.452
I sprayed Roundup for the government for 38 years, and it ruined my lungs.

00:16:28.452 --> 00:16:34.819
I'm on the donor list.

00:16:35.564 --> 00:16:51.719
The doctors say if I don't get these lungs, I'm going to die.

00:16:51.719 --> 00:17:07.689
' I asked, 'Do you believe Jesus will heal you?

00:17:07.689 --> 00:17:18.374
' He just shook his head, looking dumbfounded.

00:17:28.015 --> 00:17:35.080
He didn't give me a straight answer; he just looked at the ground.

00:17:39.053 --> 00:17:45.795
I asked, 'Can I lay hands on you?

00:17:45.795 --> 00:18:01.329
' He looked at me like I was weirding him out.

00:18:01.329 --> 00:18:25.474
I said, 'I can just pray for you,' and he said that was fine, I could touch his shoulder.

00:18:25.474 --> 00:18:57.315
I put my hand on his shoulder and said, 'I'm going to say a prayer for you and we're going to believe God.

00:19:08.679 --> 00:19:17.280
I believe with all my heart that today you're going to get healed because Jesus told me to pray for you.

00:19:17.280 --> 00:19:49.954
' I said, 'I speak to your lungs to be healed in the name of Jesus, and I command new lungs to go inside your body.

00:19:49.954 --> 00:19:58.480
' I didn't ask; I commanded them.

00:20:02.599 --> 00:20:25.336
I touched his chest and said, 'I command you to be healed and I command new lungs to come back into your body.

00:20:25.336 --> 00:20:35.183
' I didn't feel anything.

00:20:35.447 --> 00:20:45.689
I thought it was like touching a cold stove.

00:20:45.689 --> 00:20:54.320
I said, 'I believe you're healed.

00:20:54.320 --> 00:21:00.116
Have a blessed day.

00:21:00.116 --> 00:21:09.707
' He thanked me and walked away.

00:21:17.367 --> 00:21:20.520
I said, 'Lord, I obeyed you.

00:21:20.520 --> 00:21:25.969
Now it's your job.

00:21:25.969 --> 00:21:47.253
' About a week later, this man ran up to me in the yard.

00:22:03.752 --> 00:22:04.040
I did not recognize him.

00:22:05.860 --> 00:22:14.020
He said, 'Sir, do you remember me?

00:22:14.020 --> 00:22:28.506
' I said, 'No, I've never seen you before.

00:22:28.506 --> 00:22:34.954
' He said, 'I'm the man you prayed for!

00:22:34.954 --> 00:22:46.279
' I said, 'My goodness, sir, look at you!

00:22:46.279 --> 00:22:54.919
' His skin was completely normal.

00:22:54.919 --> 00:23:08.013
He had color back in his skin and looked healthy.

00:23:21.550 --> 00:23:21.945
He said, 'I was healed when you prayed for me.

00:23:31.091 --> 00:23:40.792
I went back to the doctor, and the doctor asked what I did.

00:23:52.879 --> 00:23:53.280
He said I have two brand-new lungs.

00:23:53.280 --> 00:24:04.040
' They took him off the donor list.

00:24:16.214 --> 00:24:16.489
He had no oxygen tank and was walking around normally.

00:24:22.991 --> 00:24:25.627
He came back to thank me.

00:24:25.627 --> 00:24:33.180
We eventually led him to Jesus.

00:24:33.180 --> 00:24:48.190
He used to walk around the neighborhood fast with his little cane.

00:24:48.190 --> 00:25:07.185
He wanted peaches, so I gave him some from my trees.

00:25:13.774 --> 00:25:15.279
It was an amazing testimony.

00:25:15.279 --> 00:25:39.187
But after a period of time—this went on for a few years—he started walking slow again.

00:25:39.187 --> 00:25:59.636
He got that ashy look and the tubes in his nose again.

00:25:59.636 --> 00:26:39.399
What I'm trying to say is you can get a healing, but if you don't get a foundation in the Word of God, the enemy comes back.

00:26:50.200 --> 00:27:07.009
The Bible says he goes away for a season, but he returns to the house he came from.

00:27:07.009 --> 00:27:52.039
If you don't have the Word inside you to know that 'by His stripes you are healed,' when the devil tries to bring that sickness back, you have to resist him.

00:27:52.039 --> 00:28:15.221
You have to stand and say, 'I am not accepting your poo-poo package on my front porch again.

00:28:15.221 --> 00:28:31.880
' If you don't have a foundation, you can't keep your healing.

00:28:31.880 --> 00:29:12.607
You need a root of the Word deep in your heart so that when the devil comes like a roaring lion, you say, 'You're not coming back on my land.

00:29:12.607 --> 00:29:28.040
' Great healing miracles and demonstrations of the Spirit are coming.

00:29:28.040 --> 00:29:54.328
Many of you will be healed, but the only way you'll keep it is by having a revelation of who you are in Christ.

00:29:54.328 --> 00:30:01.126
You've got to renew your mind daily.

00:30:10.248 --> 00:30:13.036
You can't just stay on the milk of the Word.

00:30:13.036 --> 00:30:24.293
It's time to go from the milk to the meat.

00:30:24.293 --> 00:30:43.960
It's time to get some teeth and a backbone and stand up for what the Word says.

00:30:47.880 --> 00:31:09.320
The devil can't devour the one who has a foundation in the Word of God.

00:31:13.103 --> 00:31:36.885
I had a vision where babies across America were in soiled diapers with flies buzzing around them.

00:31:36.885 --> 00:31:46.123
They were crying, wanting their diapers changed.

00:31:46.123 --> 00:32:10.480
They were spiritual babies, but the Lord wants to grow you up.

00:32:10.480 --> 00:32:46.360
Stand therefore, so you have a backbone against the devil to say, 'You're not robbing me anymore.

00:32:46.360 --> 00:33:03.1000
' I'm trying to teach you to take communion daily.

00:33:03.1000 --> 00:33:40.014
When your house is built upon the solid rock, the winds and waves of life will not knock you down.

00:33:40.014 --> 00:33:53.639
There are storms, but there is also glory.

00:34:17.967 --> 00:34:52.960
I don't want to hear that you were healed and then lost it because the devil came to test you.

00:34:52.960 --> 00:35:19.053
You've got to learn how to stand.

00:35:19.053 --> 00:36:34.700
Get the Word down inside your heart and you will be able to clean his clock.

00:36:34.700 --> 00:37:40.150
The Lord told me he wants you to believe for bigger.

00:37:40.160 --> 00:37:55.839
2024 is not over yet.

00:37:55.839 --> 00:38:31.318
God specializes in the impossible.

00:38:31.318 --> 00:38:57.033
He is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:39:13.691 --> 00:39:22.839
The same Jesus who healed the sick 2,000 years ago will heal your body today.

00:39:22.839 --> 00:39:47.636
I want to agree with you for your miracle.

00:39:47.636 --> 00:40:02.560
Don't let one more day pass without believing.

00:40:02.560 --> 00:40:09.160
Faith is an act.

00:40:09.160 --> 00:40:16.960
Do what you couldn't do before.

00:40:16.960 --> 00:40:26.800
Today is your day for your miracle.

00:40:26.800 --> 00:40:36.1000
We're going to take communion.

00:40:36.1000 --> 00:40:48.068
This is the meal that heals.

00:40:48.068 --> 00:41:01.987
We are joint heirs with him.

00:41:01.987 --> 00:41:17.025
Sickness and disease can't stay because God is a healer.

00:41:17.025 --> 00:41:37.692
Galatians 3:13 says Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

00:41:37.692 --> 00:41:47.880
I receive what he did today.

00:41:47.880 --> 00:41:56.534
I call myself healed.

00:42:08.956 --> 00:42:09.200
I call myself well.

00:42:09.200 --> 00:42:18.999
Your mountain needs to hear your voice.

00:42:18.999 --> 00:42:40.286
I can't believe for you; you have to speak to your own mountain.

00:42:40.286 --> 00:42:58.100
Speak to cancer, diabetes, depression, or anxiety and tell it to go.

00:42:58.100 --> 00:43:44.440
Every knee must bow to the name of Jesus.

00:43:44.440 --> 00:44:11.345
Cancer is a name, and it must bow.

00:44:11.345 --> 00:44:28.000
Heart disease is a name, and it must bow.

00:44:32.173 --> 00:44:42.446
The fire is inside you to drive out disease.

00:44:42.446 --> 00:44:51.559
By his stripes, we are healed.

00:44:51.559 --> 00:45:16.103
Father, I thank you for this body that was broken for me.

00:45:16.103 --> 00:45:28.630
I take this, and I am healed.

00:45:28.630 --> 00:45:59.412
This is the meal that heals, and I have a covenant of healing and prosperity.

00:45:59.412 --> 00:46:10.257
I have the mind of Christ.

00:46:10.257 --> 00:46:32.053
God has not given me a spirit of fear, but of power, love, and a sound mind.

00:46:32.053 --> 00:46:36.287
I receive his peace.

00:46:36.287 --> 00:46:45.839
I cast down every imagination that exalts itself against the Word of God.

00:46:59.605 --> 00:46:59.920
I refuse to fear.

00:46:59.920 --> 00:47:20.747
I have a mind full of joy and the fruit of the Spirit.

00:47:38.191 --> 00:47:41.560
I can do what the Bible says I can do.

00:47:41.560 --> 00:47:53.670
Father, we take this body and thank you that we are whole.

00:47:53.670 --> 00:48:31.653
We take this blood and thank you that our sins are cast into the sea of forgetfulness.

00:48:31.653 --> 00:48:36.360
If you make much of the blood, the blood will make much of you.

00:48:50.039 --> 00:48:52.200
I enter boldly into the courtroom of heaven.

00:48:52.200 --> 00:49:20.975
Jesus is my advocate and is making intercession for me right now.

00:49:20.975 --> 00:49:50.820
Father, we come to your throne and want to sit at your feet.

00:49:50.820 --> 00:50:02.280
We want to hear you breathe.

00:50:02.280 --> 00:50:22.660
As childlike faith, we crawl into your lap and say, 'Abba, Father.

00:50:22.660 --> 00:50:52.300
' We want a deeper revelation of who you are—our Great Physician and Jehovah Jireh.

00:50:52.300 --> 00:50:59.359
You supply all our needs.

00:50:59.359 --> 00:51:13.644
We just rest in your arms, listening to your heartbeat.

00:51:30.670 --> 00:51:30.985
I love you, Lord.

00:51:30.985 --> 00:51:38.862
I have no other.

00:51:38.862 --> 00:51:42.430
I'll never forsake you.

00:51:42.430 --> 00:51:55.867
There is fullness of peace and joy in Him.

00:51:55.867 --> 00:52:12.713
Lay your baggage at His feet and crawl into His lap.

00:52:12.713 --> 00:52:22.220
Practice the presence of the Lord.

00:52:22.220 --> 00:52:38.749
We are strong in the Lord, not in ourselves.

00:52:38.749 --> 00:52:47.222
A good father never turns his child away.

00:52:53.064 --> 00:53:02.951
He picks you up and embraces you when you are hurting.

00:53:14.924 --> 00:53:18.382
The Lord knows every pain and every wound from people's words.

00:53:18.382 --> 00:53:32.150
Even when you sin, run to God, for he is rich in mercy.

00:53:37.619 --> 00:53:45.183
Like the prodigal son, the Father is waiting with open arms.

00:53:45.183 --> 00:54:06.267
Don't let the devil lie to you; there is nothing too big for God to forgive.

00:54:06.267 --> 00:54:15.170
He's waiting for you to come home.

00:54:16.777 --> 00:54:26.750
He doesn't see you as an adult; you're his child.

00:54:26.750 --> 00:54:30.457
He will brush you off and hold you.

00:54:30.457 --> 00:54:58.651
I don't know who that is for today, but the Lord wanted you to know his heart.

00:54:58.651 --> 00:55:03.656
God is love.

00:55:05.199 --> 00:55:24.582
He corrects those he loves because he doesn't want anyone to go to hell.

00:55:30.925 --> 00:55:32.091
He wants all to come to repentance.

00:55:32.091 --> 00:55:35.599
Today is your day.

00:55:35.599 --> 00:55:43.475
Father, I'm coming home.

00:55:43.475 --> 00:55:46.575
Cleanse me and forgive me.

00:55:46.575 --> 00:55:51.015
I want a day-to-day relationship with you.

00:55:52.263 --> 00:56:10.920
I thank you, Holy Spirit, for ministering to those around me right now.

00:56:13.390 --> 00:56:33.549
I pray for a fresh touch of your fire and peace on their lives.

00:56:43.736 --> 00:56:57.746
For those who are wore out, take his yoke upon you, for his burden is light.

00:57:06.153 --> 00:57:16.507
I remember when I was battling depression and struggling in my marriage.

00:57:16.796 --> 00:57:33.639
I went to a church service and Jesus walked in through a massive portal.

00:57:33.639 --> 00:57:54.400
I could see the great cloud of witnesses—our loved ones who have gone before us.

00:57:54.400 --> 00:58:00.748
Jesus walked up to me.

00:58:00.748 --> 00:58:10.231
He had a beautiful robe and leather sandals.

00:58:10.231 --> 00:58:53.377
He showed me that I was inside a box, and he said my thinking was toxic because I was thinking too much on the wrong things.

00:58:53.377 --> 00:59:18.609
He removed the lid and told me his yoke is easy.

00:59:18.609 --> 00:59:27.160
He wanted me to be free.

00:59:27.160 --> 00:59:44.720
He smiled at me with an expression of love that melts you.

00:59:48.622 --> 01:00:04.559
I tell you these things to encourage you and fan your flames.

01:00:14.219 --> 01:00:16.440
The Lord told me to give you a refreshing.

01:00:16.440 --> 01:00:26.240
I hope this comes across the screen.

01:00:26.240 --> 01:00:45.146
This is my prayer time, and I'm letting you be a part of it.

01:00:45.146 --> 01:00:55.079
If you humble yourself, he will visit you.

01:00:55.079 --> 01:01:08.020
He is more real to me than this table.

01:01:08.020 --> 01:01:18.400
Father, I thank you for these people.

01:01:38.100 --> 01:01:38.450
I take authority over any demonic attack against this nation.

01:01:38.450 --> 01:01:48.590
No weapon formed against us shall prosper.

01:01:48.590 --> 01:01:55.869
We plead the blood over every household.

01:02:10.430 --> 01:02:16.366
We condemn the words spoken against us; they will not bear fruit.

01:02:17.946 --> 01:02:30.200
We thank you for your angels watching over us.

01:02:30.200 --> 01:02:47.120
I call for finances from the north, south, east, and west.

01:02:47.120 --> 01:03:00.142
Satan, let go of the money in Jesus' name.

01:03:02.253 --> 01:03:21.480
We call for cryptos like XRP to go up in value to bring blessing to households.

01:03:21.480 --> 01:03:34.690
We speak life over jobs and promotions.

01:03:46.860 --> 01:03:48.417
We pray for restoration in marriages and call the children home.

01:03:48.417 --> 01:04:09.148
We speak to the blinders on the eyes of unsaved loved ones and call them saved.

01:04:11.435 --> 01:04:28.150
We praise you for financial blessing, health, and mental soundness.

01:04:28.150 --> 01:04:50.640
We call for godly leadership in this nation and a move of your Spirit like never before.

01:04:53.093 --> 01:04:58.491
We give you all the glory.

01:04:58.491 --> 01:04:59.657
Amen.

01:04:59.657 --> 01:05:07.048
I'll do another video tomorrow.

01:05:07.048 --> 01:05:14.119
Please like and subscribe.

01:05:58.110 --> 01:06:01.449
Jesus is coming soon.

01:06:01.449 --> 01:06:10.480
Morning, night, or noon, many will meet their doom.

01:06:10.480 --> 01:07:00.933
Trumpets will surely sound; all of the dead shall rise.

01:07:00.933 --> 01:07:15.386
Righteous, meet in the sky, going where no one dies.

01:07:15.386 --> 01:07:18.044
Heavenward bound.

01:07:18.044 --> 01:07:22.359
He's coming soon.

01:07:22.359 --> 01:07:26.440
Put a smile on your face.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Jesus loves you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
God bless you.
